                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Detective Policeman M</hi>). I was called by a railway constable, and took the prisoner outside the station—he had a brown paper parcel, which he appeared ashamed of—it contained a dirty shirt and three paper collars.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I thought the bag did not belong to anybody, or else I would not have taken it. I was watching under the portico, think<lb></lb>ing somebody might come and claim it.</p>
